I've got ten minutes of sunlamp...

15
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:24,600
All right,
I'll do the sunlamp on the train.

16
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:29,700
Of course I'm alone.
She was an hour ago.

17
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,300
I've got to do it.

18
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:37,000
Call Charlie. He likes to take a nap
when there's going to be trouble.

19
